data.description: OPEN HOUSE - 4/20/24 1-3PM.  Welcome home to this Large 2 story corner lot home! At entry, you will notice the open concept floor plan with beautiful vinyl flooring throughout the bottom level. Many great features including a large family room with a gas fireplace and a large eat in kitchen with plenty of space for cooking and entertaining.  The second floor offers a Large Loft, 2 Large bedrooms, and a huge master suite with a walk in closet and private bathroom. Don't forget to make your way out back to see the massive fenced in yard! This home is move-in ready and waiting to welcome its new owners.
